The migrator (drizzle's better-sqlite3 migrator) runs each migration file inside a transaction. The DB connection is opened with `PRAGMA foreign_keys = ON` (set in client.ts). Here is how migrations run today:
```ts
import { migrate } from "drizzle-orm/better-sqlite3/migrator";
import { db } from "./client.js";
